<section class="section reveal" id="why-botpilot" style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent,color-mix(in srgb,var(--green) 2%,transparent),transparent)">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="sl">Why BotPilot</div>
      <h2>Not another cloud bot</h2>
      <p>BotPilot runs directly on your device. No servers, no browser extensions, no API tokens.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-ico"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></div><h3>No Credentials Needed</h3><p>You never enter your Instagram password into BotPilot. It taps the real app already logged in on your phone.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-ico"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div><h3>Very Low Detection Risk</h3><p>Uses the real Instagram app on a real device: no API calls, no browser fingerprints, no headless sessions.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-ico"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/><line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"/><line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"/></svg></div><h3>Works with 2FA</h3><p>Since BotPilot controls the app you're already signed into, two-factor auth is never an issue.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-ico"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div><h3>No Data Leaves Your Device</h3><p>No screenshots, no server connections, no analytics sent anywhere. Everything stays on your phone.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-ico"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4" y1="21" x2="4" y2="14"/><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="4" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="20" y1="21" x2="20" y2="16"/><line x1="20" y1="12" x2="20" y2="3"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="7" y2="14"/><line x1="9" y1="8" x2="15" y2="8"/><line x1="17" y1="16" x2="23" y2="16"/></svg></div><h3>Fully Configurable</h3><p>Every interaction has its own rate slider. Choose from five smart speed modes with randomized delays for natural pacing.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-ico"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg></div><h3>GIF Comments: The Flagship</h3><p>Picks a random trending GIF from Instagram's own picker and posts it as a comment. No AI server, no keyword generation.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

